item.dc:creator: @IP1 IP
item.description:
@IP1 wrote:

Hmm, well I’m not used to how Deltascape works.

However…

When pressing one of the three options (Varrock, Edgeville, Mage Bank), click one and see where you are teleported to. The EXACT coords, don’t move a space. Then do ::mypos or ::coords or however you find out your player Coordinates and search that in client.java.

Then copy it and paste it for the next set of three options.
